Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Hei, di mana orang-orang itu?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Bos.{\b0}
