Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Lelah.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ada apa dengan penampilanmu ini?{\b0}
