Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Terima kasih semuanya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Kalian jangan sampai terlambat, ya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ikutilah dengan baik.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Baik, Elbaf yang sudah lama dinanti-nantikan.{\b0}
