Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Dr. Vegapunk sedang meneliti Void Century.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ini adalah tindakan menghubungi Marijoa.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ternyata inilah alasan CP datang menyelidiki berkali-kali.{\b0}
