Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Namun, aku punya firasat buruk.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Pythagoras.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Perhatikan pengamatan gelombang radio nirkabel dan tingkat air bawah tanah.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku mengerti.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apakah ada hubungannya dengan Mother Flame yang dicuri?{\b0}
