Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Namun, makin dekat maka akan makin gelap.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Apa sebenarnya Pemerintah Dunia itu?{\b0}
