Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Tubuh Asli, apa yang sedang kau lakukan di sini?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Ternyata York.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Sama seperti biasanya.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\b1}Aku sedang melakukan uji coba aktivasi Mother Flame.{\b0}
